# pdf_file_manager Version Sync

When updating `ai_study_buddy/pdf_file_manager/CHANGELOG.md` with a new version bump, always update the version line in `ai_study_buddy/pdf_file_manager/README.md` in the same change.

Checklist:
- If changelog adds a new `vX.Y.Z` section, set `README.md` `**Version: vX.Y.Z**` to the same version.
- Do not leave changelog and README on different versions.
